```

#### `fine.ai.thread(threadId)`

Refers to an existing thread.

- `.data` ‚Äî fetch thread metadata
- `.messages` ‚Äî get messages in the thread
- `.update(metadata)` ‚Äî update thread metadata
- `.delete()` ‚Äî delete the thread
- `.message(...)` ‚Äî create a message in this thread

